text: Hemipilia crassicalcara is a species of plant in the family Orchidaceae. It is endemic to China. == Sources == * China Plant Specialist Group 2004. Hemipilia crassicalcara. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 21 August 2007.
